message.body: Hi Kennedy! This's Alexandra from CS. So, does nothing changed? Can I come tomorrow?
Sure! What time are you arriving?
Good! Somewhen in 11-12 am. Soon i'll be able to connect to the internet and say exactly. Will you be busy at that time?
Nope, should be home. See you then!
So, I arrive at 11.45 at 30th st station. Will you meet me there or I need to go somewhere?
Ok. Thank you very very much :) See you soon.
Are you coming here soon? Or wandering a bit first? Just trying to plan out the day
Yes, I'm somewhere here, come soon.
I think I would be soon near your home. Are you there?
